issue.title: Error during startup for gas sensor

content.raw:
Thanks for the hint to look into the release note, but I did not recognize that the system should be upgraded. I did the cleanup by deinstallating of the pre-release versions already some time ago. So I did not rerun these scripts. 

Now it works. So thanks.

‌
